high_descs: Turn around and go straight, then face right to the black table.
Pick up the apple to the right from the table.
Take the apple and move a few steps to the right to locate the sink.
Put the apple in the sink, turn the water on and then off. Pick up the apple.
Take the apple and move to the left to face the white table.
Place the apple on the table, close to the front and to the left of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Rinse the apple and place it on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the toaster then turn right and walk to the small black table.
Pick up the apple that's to the right of another apple on the small black table.
Take a step to your right so you're in front of the sink facing it.
Wash the apple in the sink then take it back out and close the tap.
Turn around and take a step then turn right and walk to the table.
Put the apple to the left of the salt shaker and below the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room and face the black table to the right of the counter.
Pick up the fruit on the left from the table.
Go right to the sink and turn to face it.
Put the fruit in the sink, turn the water on and then off and pick the fruit up from the sink.
Go left and face the white table.
Put  the fruit on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean piece of fruit on a table.
